92
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,200
The three of them are living in America.

93
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,600
Alright, I've been holding it in the whole way.

94
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:38,400
I need to use the bathroom. I'll talk to you in a bit.

95
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,080
Why are you here?

96
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,780
Xinxin, take this.

97
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,720
Come over here. I'm going to the bathroom.

98
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,160
Okay.

99
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,290
I'll talk to both of you in a minute.

100
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,320
I've missed you so much.

101
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,320
No, my sister is here.

102
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,360
Your sister is here?

103
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,760
It's fine. Why worry if your sister's here?

104
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,680
Stop it.

105
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,200
Sis!

106
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,880
Huaming.

107
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:05,520
Sis.

108
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:07,960
You haven't been mistreating my sister, have you?

109
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,760
Sis, how could I ever mistreat Xinxin?

110
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,690
I wouldn't dare.

111
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,360
I must say, you move pretty fast.

112
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:17,040
We just got back from the airport and you're already here.

113
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,600
Weren't you supposed to be with your wife and child,

114
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,800
living in America?

115
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:20,880
No, sis.

116
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,800
It's a long story. I'll tell you the details another day.

117
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:25,600
Anyway, we've already decided.

118
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:26,960
We're getting our marriage license right away.

119
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,400
Getting married right away.

120
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,800
What about your ex-wife?

121
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,520
Sister, I've made things clear with my ex-wife.

122
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,520
I went to America to accompany my child for school,

123
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,920
not to get back together with her.

124
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:38,720
Huaming, I've always had a good impression of you.

125
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,760
You cannot mistreat our Xinxin.

126
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,650
You need to follow through.

127
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,520
Don't worry, sister.

128
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,960
I will definitely treat Xinxin well.

129
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,200
I'll take full responsibility.

130
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,920
You're getting your marriage license tomorrow, right?

131
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:51,320
Good, then I'll go with you tomorrow.

132
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,160
Why do you need to come?

133
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,240
To supervise!

134
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,840
What are you, the neighborhood committee? Supervising me?

135
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,600
Xinxin.

136
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,960
Your sister is part of our family.

137
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,120
When we get our marriage certificate tomorrow,

138
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,320
having a witness present

139
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,640
who is also family makes it so special.

140
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,320
Thank you, sis. Sorry for the trouble.

141
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,000
Alright. Tomorrow then.

142
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,920
We'll meet at the entrance

143
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,680
of the Civil Affairs Bureau tomorrow.

144
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,320
Sis, you don't need to go tomorrow.

145
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,360
Why shouldn't I go?

146
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,920
I'll leave these things here. I'm going now.

147
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:16,360
Alright.

148
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,240
Take care, sis.

149
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,010
Should I take this suit?

150
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,730
Never mind, take it.

151
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,160
I'll leave a few days later.

152
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,760
No, we go together.

153
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,400
I said I'll leave a few days later.

154
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,800
No, I said we go together.

155
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:38,680
Ruirui.

156
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,280
Ruirui.

157
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:58,960
Ruirui, Daddy needs to ask you something.

158
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:00,580
Why didn't you want

159
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:03,580
